currentDoc: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

currentSuggestions.original: The US is the most powerful nation on Earth and they can't even come up with a working hover car.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: The US is the most powerful nation on Earth and they can't even come up with a working hover car.

currentSuggestions.original: What the world gets is an America that's changed in many ways.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: What the world gets is an America that's changed in many ways.

currentSuggestions.original: The U.S., the only superpower left in the world, has to learn to survive in a new world full of political intrigue and conflict.
